ies within upper bounds (a few hundred km) for which the\ninternal strength could no longer withstand tidal forces from the gravity of\nthe WD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Jun 2023 17:06:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-07"}
